{"tid":685687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"酷熱警告300小時創紀錄 遊樂設施暴曬　72.8℃燙傷學生","createTime":"2018-05-31T15:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T23:26:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"338c39c8fbeff94e77b6f1e3d7886f7874a04461","tid":685687,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:07:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180531/20406648?_ga=2.127882761.509227112.1527749548-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180531%2F20406648%3F_ga%3D2.127882761.509227112.1527749548-581282530.1504247435&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=490db8ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180531%2F20406648%3F_ga%3D2.127882761.509227112.1527749548-581282530.1504247435&h=bcd629eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180531/20406648?_ga=2.127882761.509227112.1527749548-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月31日 <br />\n<br />\n酷熱警告300小時創紀錄<br />\n遊樂設施暴曬　72.8℃燙傷學生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180531/large/31la2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180531%2Flarge%2F31la2p2.jpg&h=a28d080e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李同學觸摸輪胎後手掌疑被燙傷。簡明恩攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】踏入5月本港猶如盛夏，天文台昨錄得35.4℃，破紀錄連續14天錄得逾33℃高溫，除成為今年最高溫一天，亦取代前天的紀錄成為歷年第二高溫的5月天，酷熱天氣警告更連掛逾300小時。一名婦人與友人行玉桂山時中暑，送院治理後情況危殆；而市區遊樂場設施在暴曬下升溫，有橡膠輪胎表面溫度達72.8℃，隨時燙傷兒童。<br />\n記者：溫瑞麟　胡恩宏　劉漢權<br />\n<br />\n酷熱天氣警告由本月18日早上6時45分發出，至昨夜持續逾300小時，成為2000年有酷熱天氣警告以來最長紀錄，打破2007年維持286小時10分鐘，同時刷新5月份最多酷熱警告紀錄。新界多處地區錄得高溫，大美督及打鼓嶺均錄得逾36℃高溫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180531/large/31la2p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180531%2Flarge%2F31la2p3.jpg&h=6e270890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■遊樂場輪胎表面達72.8℃。簡明恩攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180531/large/31la2p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180531%2Flarge%2F31la2p4.jpg&h=64e20189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中暑婦人送院搶救。劉漢權攝<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n婦人行山中暑危殆<br />\n<br />\n一名54歲姓羅家庭主婦與朋友一行約4人，昨中午由香港仔利東邨出發到玉桂山行山，至下午1時許，羅在鴨脷排附近疑暴曬中暑不適，頭暈昏迷，友人報警。飛行服務隊派出直升機將事主送往醫院，經深切治療部搶救後情況危殆，事發時天文台在香港仔錄得34℃高溫。另外，昨午3時許一名20歲姓朱女子於石澳鶴嘴道行山時亦出現中暑症狀不適，即場接受治理後無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高溫暴曬下，除了在郊外活動有危險，市區的露天兒童遊樂設施亦隱藏危機。《蘋果》昨午3時許用溫度計量度，發現黃大仙下邨兒童遊樂場一個供攀爬的橡膠黑輪胎，表面溫度高達72.8℃，而場內的金屬滑梯及遊樂設施金屬面板，表面溫度分別達42.7℃及51.7℃，若不為意觸摸到，隨時燙傷皮膚。附近的鳳德公園遊樂場亦悶熱如「蒸籠」，用作保護小童的膠地墊溫度高達66.6℃，至於旁邊供市民休息的木凳，表面溫度同樣達59.1℃。<br />\n<br />\n李同學認為天氣炎熱不宜於戶外遊樂場玩耍，他觸摸遊樂場橡膠黑輪胎十多秒感受溫度，起初不覺得太熱，但隨即感到刺痛，察看手掌竟被燙紅，懷疑已經輕微燙傷。由於熱浪驚人，兩個遊樂場都未見有人玩耍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幼童戴黑超等校車<br />\n<br />\n烈日當空，市民為免曬傷各出奇謀，讀幼稚園的林小朋友戴上太陽眼鏡等候校車，並指會「留喺室內，飲多啲凍水」。市民方小姐同樣戴上太陽眼鏡外出，她表示外出時一定會塗防曬霜和戴帽，並盡量留在家中嘆冷氣。天文台預測，未來兩日天氣仍然酷熱，至周末有驟雨。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180531/large/a0201a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180531%2Flarge%2Fa0201a.gif&h=6b8fcd0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n稻田乾到裂　農夫修井自救"},{"pid":"af7a660991141d296bf51ac845b088afa9c7a326","tid":685687,"uid":129521,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T19:24:14.000Z","msg":"00後<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/032413_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F032413_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=247c9b58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0cbc23086a9681b2d9bc635db849bf9881aad58","tid":685687,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T19:27:15.000Z","msg":"熱屎辣辣仲咁多人去行山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f1ff5071618ea9b4426c5c795e1574c885d639","tid":685687,"uid":50060,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T19:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3ca105c5968fd1b6802cf64a41cc59a2d56439","tid":685687,"uid":8175,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T19:55:00.000Z","msg":"班廢中係咪on9 咁撚熱先走黎行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0e7602040d126b0a5dd2b45dd5e2f1a1e42044","tid":685687,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b3ca105c5968fd1b6802cf64a41cc59a2d56439","tid":685687,"uid":8175,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T19:55:00.000Z","msg":"班廢中係咪on9 咁撚熱先走黎行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T21:39:33.000Z","msg":"熱屎辣辣返工咪一樣on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8716aa3145d5226ddfd3a3be9a95c7834fbb622c","tid":685687,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T23:23:23.000Z","msg":"王心凌新素材<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c67d704df85c0575ac31f18a2c9574ff2cf0129","tid":685687,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c0e7602040d126b0a5dd2b45dd5e2f1a1e42044","tid":685687,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b3ca105c5968fd1b6802cf64a41c